EN: This land is suitable for growing various crops.

ZH: 农民们在早春季节播种各种作物。
EN: Farmers sow various crops in early spring.

ZH: 由于干旱，今年的作物收成不太好。
EN: Due to drought, the crop yield is not very good this year.

