EN: The big storm caused severe damage to the crops in this area.

ZH: 高温天气不利于一些作物的生长。
EN: Hot weather is not conducive to the growth of certain crops.

ZH: 农民们努力采取措施，保护作物不受冻害。
EN: Farmers make efforts to protect crops from frost damage.

ZH: 这片土地的肥力非常适合种出丰收的作物。
EN: The fertility of this land is very suitable for growing productive crops.

ZH: 虫害是作物生长过程中的常见问题之一。
EN: Pest infestation is one of the common problems in crop growth.

ZH: 这个温室使用先进的技术种植各种高价值的作物。
EN: This greenhouse uses advanced technology to cultivate various high-value crops.

ZH: 短暂的干旱期并不会对作物产生太大的影响。
EN: A short period of drought does not have a significant impact on crops.

ZH: 种植作物需要耕地、播种和及时的管理。
EN: Crop cultivation requires land, sowing, and timely management.
